---
// Process Section - TrailRider Gear Adventure Guide
---

<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-background">
  <div class="container max-w-5xl">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        PLAN. EQUIP. EXPLORE.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Your journey to remote adventures starts here
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps -->
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-8 group">
        <div class="text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-display font-bold text-text opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity flex-shrink-0">
          01
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 pt-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4">PLAN YOUR ADVENTURE</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-text-muted">
            Research your destination, check weather conditions, and identify the gear you'll need for your specific hunting or fishing expedition. Consider terrain difficulty, distance, and duration.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-8 group">
        <div class="text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-display font-bold text-text opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity flex-shrink-0">
          02
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 pt-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4">EQUIP YOUR E-BIKE</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-text-muted">
            Choose the right accessories for your adventure. From gun racks for hunting trips to rod holders for remote fishing spots, we've tested the gear that performs in real wilderness conditions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-8 group">
        <div class="text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-display font-bold text-text opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity flex-shrink-0">
          03
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 pt-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4">EXPLORE THE WILD</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-text-muted">
            Access remote hunting grounds and fishing spots that others can't reach. Your e-bike opens up new possibilities for outdoor adventures, taking you deeper into the wilderness with less effort.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-20">
      <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-10 py-5 bg-text text-background rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-text/90 hover:scale-105 transition-all">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M4 10H16M16 10L11 5M16 10L11 15"></path>
        </svg>
        EXPLORE GEAR REVIEWS
      </a>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-6">
        Expert Tested • Field Approved • Adventure Ready
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
